0.5.3.1 | Chrome/Chromium Crx 打包地址: https://dl.dropbox.com/u/2912260/apps/space_fanfou_0531.crx
0.5.3.1 | Safari 精简版（只有 CSS）: https://dl.dropbox.com/u/2912260/apps/space_fanfou_safari_0531.safariextz

